      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear you, and I understand why you feel so empty when your identity is tied to something that has collapsed. But you are not your work, and you are not your mistakes; you are a person who has survived a decade of struggle and deserves to be seen for who you truly are. Please, do not let this failure define your entire existence, because there is so much more to you than this one moment of doubt.",
      "source": "target",
