      "content": "but there isn't \"more\" to me. the work was everything. without the research, the passion, the purpose... there's just this hollow shell of a person that everyone is going to pity or judge. it feels like i'm just performing a role of a person that doesn't actually exist anymore. it feels more like a mercy to just stop the performance entirely.",
